:

1. *Crkve* su uglavnom prazne u vreme pandemije. (Churches are mostly empty during the pandemic.)
2. *Crkvama* je zabranjeno da obavljaju mise. (Churches are forbidden to perform masses.)
3. *Crkvene* službe se obavljaju preko interneta. (Church services are held online.)
4. U *crkvi* je mnogo ljudi koji žele da se pokaju. (There are many people in the church who want to repent.)
5. *Crkvi* su dodeljene velike sume novca od vlade. (Large sums of money were granted to churches by the government.)